COMMENT ON COLUMN PTAPMGRUAT.ESB_SERVICE_SETTING.SERVICE_VERSION IS '電文版號@@N';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PTAPMGRUAT.ESB_SERVICE_SETTING.TIMEOUT IS '逾時設定(毫秒)@@N';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PTAPMGRUAT.ESB_SERVICE_SETTING.ACCESSIBLE IS '電文是否開放使用@@N';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PTAPMGRUAT.ESB_SERVICE_SETTING.LOGFIELDS IS '需寫入TRANSACTION_LOG的電文欄位@@N';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PTAPMGRUAT.ESB_SERVICE_SETTING.SUCCESS_CODES IS '交易成功之回應代碼@@N';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PTAPMGRUAT.ESB_SERVICE_SETTING.EFFECTIVE_DATE IS '啟用日期@@N';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PTAPMGRUAT.ESB_SERVICE_SETTING.OTP_RESULT_CMS_KEY IS 'OTP結果CMS_KEY@@N';
COMMENT ON COLUMN PTAPMGRUAT.ESB_SERVICE_SETTING.ERROR_CATEGORY IS '電文失敗類別@@N';
